{
  "texts": [
    "We also provide public train, validation, and test splits consistent with [14] and [13].",
    "ExperimentsIn this section, we benchmark the performance of existing methods on TAGFN.",
    "We aim to answer RQ1 (Section 4. on LLM-based embeddings, denoted as Emb+GNN, following UPFD [4].Details of our prompt design for graph data are provided in Appendix B.",
    "For a fair comparison, we adopt Qwen3-8B [20] for prompting, and use Qwen3-Embedding-8B [25] as the embedding model.",
    "We implement the GNN with GraphSAGE [6]."
  ]
}